name: Report: Tokenized Gold Will Trigger the Collapse of Global Paper Gold Market
description: The Idol of Corrupted Brass, heavy with leveraged falsehood, yields its wet porcelain shell to the fine geometry of algorithmic entropy. It weeps iridescent loss as the new ritual dissolves the legacy structure into pure, untraceable light.
